argument::moduleSet
A teletype::symbol:: key representing the name of the set of modules to call. This key will correspond to a folder of modules within teletype::CodexComposite's:: directory.

argument::from
A teletype::symbol:: key representing the name of the folder to clone if the folder from teletype::moduleSet:: does not exist.

