method::moduleSets
Gets the names of the teletype::moduleSets:: that currently exist.

method::directory
Gets and (persistently) sets the directory of modules for all subclasses of teletype::CodexComposite::. For further details, see link::Classes/PathStorage::.
note::Before using a subclass of teletype::CodexComposite:: for the first time, be sure to configure the path to the modules directory either through teletype::CodexComposite:: or one of its subclasses.::
code::
CodexComposite.directory_("~/Documents/sc-modules".standardizePath);
